@node SW_83 "Sword of Kas"
<pfrey@drew.bitnet>
(Note: These powers should be kept secret by the DM...see below)
Intelligence: 15
Ego: 19
Alignment: CE
+6 defender
Telepathy (even when not held)
Double damage against all creatures which are from a plane other than the Prime
