save versus wands at -5.
   The sword will especially push the user to kill helpless victims, saying that
it will offer more powers. If asked why it lied about its powers to begin with,
it will defend himself by saying that it does not want the possessor to become
too powerful. Inform the possessor that, by using this sword, he will gain more
